  "detailed_description": "<h1>ONLINE CO-OP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/db65f33c3fefa5ba75e20f0a014fc1d7.avif?t=1761035337\" width=800 height=416 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/863bc01d5b22708e005a6d3ca18faac5.webp?t=1761035337\" width=41 height=35 /></span><strong>Double the firepower! Online/Local co-op update now live!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two guns are always better than one. Dive into AK-xolotl's co-op mode with a friend, battle through hordes of enemies, share epic power-ups, and blast through levels as a lethal duo of axolotls armed to the teeth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/863bc01d5b22708e005a6d3ca18faac5.webp?t=1761035337\" width=41 height=35 /></span><strong>AK-xolotl 2.0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive update has arrived in AK-xolotl! Discover 20+ new weapons, new items, new biomes, and face off against new bosses and enemies. Major overhauls to the Axolittles, cooking, and weapon systems, plus the addition of weapon mods, bring new depth and variety to your axolotl adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/6b587257de701e1f6996eab8943a8532.avif?t=1761035337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras_big/6b587257de701e1f6996eab8943a8532.avif?t=1761035337 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/75f3346aa4236fdf2dc23fd7f9f3fb66.webp?t=1761035337\" width=782 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AK-xolotl is the <strong>ultimate</strong> top-down roguelite shooter starring the most adorable amphibian! You're an axolotl armed with an AK, that embarks on an epic rampage, shooting down anything that stands in your way. Slaughter your way through a variety of biomes and conquer randomly generated rooms, all while collecting delicious food and capturing precious baby Axolotls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ab820828ed4a53b640fba95085c89422.poster.avif?t=1761035337\" width=780 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ab820828ed4a53b640fba95085c89422.webm?t=1761035337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Channel the incredible power of Axolotls' regeneration! If you're knocked down, you will rise again from the ashes and start stronger, unlocking new weapons with each fight. Fight, die, come back stronger and fight again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ec4be1c2f9606fe5c125cb1d86e6c97e.poster.avif?t=1761035337\" width=780 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/ec4be1c2f9606fe5c125cb1d86e6c97e.webm?t=1761035337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your journey, you will find different baby Axolotls - Axolittles! Bring Axolittles back to your pond; nurturing them with love and care, they will grow up and become your next fighter with killer abilities! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/0175214b47cab3a753757ace18acb349.poster.avif?t=1761035337\" width=780 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/0175214b47cab3a753757ace18acb349.webm?t=1761035337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Slithering Sock Snakes to Giant (knife wielding) Enemy Crabs, these bosses will put your regenerative abilities to the test. Time to bring an AK-47 to a knife fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/1515b3ba7169adb65555b05a5da46ba8.poster.avif?t=1761035337\" width=780 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/1515b3ba7169adb65555b05a5da46ba8.webm?t=1761035337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find Axolotl eggs and raise new powerful Axolittles by turning them into highly specialized little killing machines. Take their firepower to the next level by cooking up permanent, stat-improving recipes. Take no prisoners, eat everything and become unstoppable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/33649aa373419a17ab59bc8f55844c02.poster.avif?t=1761035337\" width=780 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/33649aa373419a17ab59bc8f55844c02.webm?t=1761035337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight up close with the Axe-alotl or or set your Phaser to “murder”... your playstyle is your pick! Take your firepower to the next level with mighty power-ups like Mjolnir, Gamer Juice or…Cousin Carl?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/863bc01d5b22708e005a6d3ca18faac5.webp?t=1761035337\" width=41 height=35 /></span><strong>Double the firepower! Online/Local co-op update now live!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two guns are always better than one. Dive into AK-xolotl's co-op mode with a friend, battle through hordes of enemies, share epic power-ups, and blast through levels as a lethal duo of axolotls armed to the teeth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/863bc01d5b22708e005a6d3ca18faac5.webp?t=1761035337\" width=41 height=35 /></span><strong>AK-xolotl 2.0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive update has arrived in AK-xolotl! Discover 20+ new weapons, new items, new biomes, and face off against new bosses and enemies. Major overhauls to the Axolittles, cooking, and weapon systems, plus the addition of weapon mods, bring new depth and variety to your axolotl adventures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/6b587257de701e1f6996eab8943a8532.avif?t=1761035337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras_big/6b587257de701e1f6996eab8943a8532.avif?t=1761035337 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479140/extras/75f3346aa4236fdf2dc23fd7f9f3fb66.webp?t=1761035337\" width=782 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AK-xolotl is the <